    "type": "message",
    "text": "And one thing right off the bat that creates that 100+ hour training time is the vast number of API's.You can see it in Apple's OSX as well, there are too many thousands of API's, far more than you need. If we had interchangeable parts in software like machinery you wouldn't need such elaborate API sets and engines.",
